Comment 1: Hello Lavanya, Your call to authenp is done statically. To make this work you need to define you method as static. in gravity.php - 
```text
public static function authenp($course_id)
```
 Alternatively if you don't want to call it statically you have to createa  new gravity object 
```text
$gravity = new gravity();


$acc = $gravity->authenp($courseid);
```
